          {
            "type": "prose",
            "text": "Two biometric subsystems were deployed within the AI Service container: the STL-trained EfficientNet-B0 facial embedder and the sample-then-lock fingerprint fuzzy extractor. The facial embedder was deployed as a frozen checkpoint produced at the end of a grid search over the STL linkability weight λ and optimization margin, with the best configuration selected by cancelable-domain False Match Rate (FMR) rather than raw Equal Error Rate (EER)."
          },
          {
