          {
            "type": "prose",
            "text": "The fingerprint fuzzy extractor operated on binarized DeepPrint minutiae descriptors under the Sample-then-Lock construction. Its two structural parameters: (a) locker count L and (b) feature bits per locker k, were selected from a grid search over L ∈ {512, 1024, 2048} and k ∈ {4, 8, 16}, evaluated across voting-ratio-stratified quality tiers, yielding a deployed configuration of L = 1024, k = 8."
          },
